0246cb3bf6bd57b1d216c7572f58699f7a03","tid":893981,"uid":77092,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"1fb1296031232a868eb471dff05d71f38f77c623","tid":893981,"uid":139573,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T11:07:38.000Z","msg":"friend到喪禮送左48支烈酒比古龍做陪葬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T11:57:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T12:01:27.000Z","msg":"古龍名利雙收後，常常與倪匡一餐飯就喝掉5瓶XO，翌日兩人結伴去醫院吊鹽水<br />\n倪匡咁都可以咁長命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T14:23:38.000Z","msg":"那天弔祭時，眾人淚灑靈堂。倪匡哭得傷心，女作家三毛在旁摟著他，安慰他。蓋棺前，古龍這幫朋友中，不知是誰提議，不如當著古龍的面，把酒喝掉，古龍才會高興。這一提議，眾人連連叫好。<br />\n<br />\n於是，大家打開酒蓋，猛喝，每瓶酒都喝了一半，就醉了。眾人還請古龍喝，結果往他嘴裡倒酒，古龍的嘴似乎還真的微微張開一下，酒汩汩往嘴裡流，突然紅彤彤的鮮血，從嘴裡噴湧而墥，在邊上的倪匡和三毛、高信疆，都一陣驚嚇。<br />\n<br />\n係殯儀館到飲酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n重要倒埋落條屍到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e49904e49e6ec550d66a887750c41a1ecc9b90f","tid":893981,"uid":217728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T14:27:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 淨係想睇佢既作品"},{"pid":"0e6afdabf67be47f8d94479d46ee30bc1fba95db","tid":893981,"uid":110832,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T14:31:37.000Z","msg":"明報出手低<br />\n垃圾老闆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n送大禮純粹因為倪匡同佢老友"},{"pid":"fdec29100bbe7bb4ad8878aedfabba77905a3b78","tid":893981,"uid":110832,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T14:34:32.000Z","msg":"金庸根本君子劍<br />\n對自己朋友就好<br />\n對其他人就虛偽"},{"pid":"8f82cea1993fe279fb6d981b98e4cc0acb234481","tid":893981,"uid":653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d923